00:25:44,510 --> 00:25:45,829
In your project proposal,

584
00:25:45,829 --> 00:25:47,750
there are two commercial blocks

585
00:25:48,030 --> 00:25:49,669
and an elderly care facility.

586
00:25:50,510 --> 00:25:51,990
So I'm wondering if

587
00:25:52,189 --> 00:25:53,510
we're able to work on
the smart home elements

588
00:25:54,070 --> 00:25:55,629
for the three projects.

589
00:25:58,990 --> 00:25:59,510
Xiang Qian,

590
00:25:59,629 --> 00:26:00,429
you two

591
00:26:01,030 --> 00:26:02,189
are planning ahead, huh?

592
00:26:02,750 --> 00:26:04,109
I haven't won the bid yet,

593
00:26:04,470 --> 00:26:05,030
and here you are

594
00:26:05,070 --> 00:26:05,990
discussing business with me.

595
00:26:08,109 --> 00:26:09,070
It's because

596
00:26:09,510 --> 00:26:10,829
we're just starting up.

597
00:26:10,869 --> 00:26:12,149
If we don't get a head-start,

598
00:26:12,270 --> 00:26:13,710
how would we win the bid?

599
00:26:14,470 --> 00:26:15,389
Yes, yes.

600
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:17,669
I'll be frank with you.

601
00:26:18,710 --> 00:26:19,710
The possibility of us

602
00:26:20,189 --> 00:26:21,070
winning the bid

603
00:26:21,149 --> 00:26:22,189
is pretty high.

604
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:24,149
But,

605
00:26:24,189 --> 00:26:25,869
currently, many good companies

606
00:26:26,389 --> 00:26:27,790
are eyeing the outsourced projects.

607
00:26:28,429 --> 00:26:30,349
Moreover, a lot of them
are well established.

608
00:26:31,710 --> 00:26:33,669
So, we can only employ

609
00:26:34,189 --> 00:26:36,030
a unified public bidding.

610
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:38,109
This way, we won't ruffle
anyone's feathers

611
00:26:38,429 --> 00:26:39,829
and also be responsible
to the government.

612
00:26:40,750 --> 00:26:41,550
It will be decided

613
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,510
using each company's proposal
and quotation.

614
00:26:43,990 --> 00:26:44,909
If yours is good,

615
00:26:45,470 --> 00:26:46,470
I'm all for it.

616
00:26:47,070 --> 00:26:49,109
But if it's not favorable,

617
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,149
I can't make a case for it.

618
00:26:52,790 --> 00:26:53,429
Understood.

619
00:26:53,589 --> 00:26:55,070
I know that is the best way.

620
00:26:55,149 --> 00:26:55,829
Well...

621
00:26:56,950 --> 00:26:57,710
We should separate public
from personal interests.

622
00:26:58,109 --> 00:26:59,310
So we...

623
00:27:00,109 --> 00:27:01,389
We'll fight for it with our proposal,

624
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,109
yes?

625
00:27:02,470 --> 00:27:03,189
Although

626
00:27:03,550 --> 00:27:04,629
speaking in private,

627
00:27:05,589 --> 00:27:06,990
we are family after all.

628
00:27:07,510 --> 00:27:08,349
I...

629
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:10,310
will be inclined

630
00:27:10,589 --> 00:27:11,950
to have some preference.

631
00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:15,070
As long as I'm not put in
too difficult a position.

632
00:27:15,710 --> 00:27:16,429
No, no,

633
00:27:16,429 --> 00:27:17,470
that will not happen.

634
00:27:19,189 --> 00:27:20,310
Here, Mr. Jiang.

635
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:22,030
Allow me to toast to you.

636
00:27:23,389 --> 00:27:24,270
Well,

637
00:27:24,669 --> 00:27:25,790
we are a small company

638
00:27:25,829 --> 00:27:26,470
just starting out.

639
00:27:26,629 --> 00:27:27,710
I hope you'll take us

640
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:28,629
under your wing.

641
00:27:29,230 --> 00:27:30,589
We don't treat family members
as strangers.

642
00:27:31,030 --> 00:27:32,389
We should share our resources.

643
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:34,310
You never know.

644
00:27:34,909 --> 00:27:35,829
In the future,

645
00:27:36,070 --> 00:27:37,109
I might require your assistance.

646
00:27:37,429 --> 00:27:38,230
Come on now.

647
00:27:38,510 --> 00:27:40,389
Feel free to tell us
if you need anything.

648
00:27:42,230 --> 00:27:42,669
Here.

649
00:27:42,829 --> 00:27:43,429
I won't drink.

650
00:27:43,429 --> 00:27:43,990
I'm the driver.

651
00:27:43,990 --> 00:27:45,510
Yes, yes, she's driving today.

652
00:27:45,669 --> 00:27:46,669
- Bottoms up.
- Be my guest.

