00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:57,840
(Ming Wei)

654
00:28:05,510 --> 00:28:06,750
Hello, Ming Wei.

655
00:28:07,310 --> 00:28:08,550
I was in a meeting.

656
00:28:08,669 --> 00:28:09,990
Why did you call me?

657
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:13,470
I asked you to help me

658
00:28:13,589 --> 00:28:15,030
find someone

659
00:28:15,109 --> 00:28:16,270
to handle the higher-ups.

660
00:28:17,750 --> 00:28:18,669
I've found

661
00:28:19,109 --> 00:28:20,829
a suitable candidate.

662
00:28:21,869 --> 00:28:22,470
Who is it?

663
00:28:24,149 --> 00:28:27,230
You could say it's a family member.

664
00:28:28,710 --> 00:28:29,429
Don't worry.

665
00:28:30,550 --> 00:28:32,230
If anything bad happens,

666
00:28:33,070 --> 00:28:34,429
they'll bear
the consequences themselves.

667
00:28:35,710 --> 00:28:37,030
We won't be implicated.

668
00:29:08,669 --> 00:29:09,470
Door unlocked.

669
00:29:11,470 --> 00:29:12,270
Xu Miao.

670
00:29:15,429 --> 00:29:16,669
What happened? Are you okay?

671
00:29:20,149 --> 00:29:21,070
I'm sorry.

672
00:29:22,109 --> 00:29:23,429
It's all my fault.

673
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:26,750
You didn't do anything wrong.

674
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,429
Why are you apologizing?

675
00:29:33,109 --> 00:29:34,230
You weren't harmed, were you?

676
00:29:41,710 --> 00:29:42,909
What exactly happened?

677
00:29:43,149 --> 00:29:44,349
Tell us.

678
00:29:45,389 --> 00:29:46,270
It's because

679
00:29:46,349 --> 00:29:47,990
of the 300 pieces of ornaments.

680
00:29:48,589 --> 00:29:49,990
They required a 5% interval fee

681
00:29:49,990 --> 00:29:51,389
to be transferred to a private account.

682
00:29:51,710 --> 00:29:53,030
So I made two labor contracts

683
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:54,189
to take out the money first.

684
00:29:54,750 --> 00:29:56,189
If you transfer money from a public
to a private account,

685
00:29:56,349 --> 00:29:57,510
the bank will investigate.

686
00:29:58,030 --> 00:29:58,909
I had explained

687
00:29:59,030 --> 00:30:00,149
to Jiang

688
00:30:00,189 --> 00:30:00,990
beforehand.

689
00:30:01,829 --> 00:30:03,230
I really don't get why

690
00:30:03,429 --> 00:30:05,070
he still chose to report it.

691
00:30:08,349 --> 00:30:09,669
He's forcing me to go back

692
00:30:09,750 --> 00:30:10,750
and plead with him.

693
00:30:14,230 --> 00:30:15,270
I'm sorry, Xu Miao.

694
00:30:15,750 --> 00:30:17,349
You got sacrificed because of me.

695
00:30:18,349 --> 00:30:18,990
Xiang Nan,

696
00:30:19,189 --> 00:30:20,869
we are beyond pleasantries.

697
00:30:22,829 --> 00:30:23,990
During my time inside,

698
00:30:24,829 --> 00:30:26,589
a lot went through my mind.

699
00:30:27,310 --> 00:30:28,389
Jiang Hongbin

700
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:29,270
is too powerful.

701
00:30:29,669 --> 00:30:31,149
We can't possibly beat him.

702
00:30:32,950 --> 00:30:33,950
So I thought

703
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:35,470
if I couldn't confront him,

704
00:30:35,669 --> 00:30:36,669
I could at least hide.

705
00:30:37,070 --> 00:30:37,669
If I run,

706
00:30:37,909 --> 00:30:39,310
at least I know I'll be safe.

707
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,349
I've got friends

708
00:30:44,389 --> 00:30:46,030
who are running a studio in Jingdezhen.

709
00:30:46,869 --> 00:30:47,950
Their local policies

710
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:49,149
have pretty good benefits.

711
00:30:50,589 --> 00:30:52,270
They've been asking me to join them.

712
00:30:54,270 --> 00:30:54,990
I...

713
00:30:55,629 --> 00:30:56,510
have agreed.

714
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,550
Can I...

715
00:31:05,030 --> 00:31:06,510
go and take a look too?

716
00:31:09,429 --> 00:31:10,909
Both of you want to leave?

717
00:31:11,550 --> 00:31:12,950
It will only be me.

718
00:31:13,629 --> 00:31:15,149
You can come with us.

719
00:31:15,669 --> 00:31:16,909
You should divorce him.

720
00:31:17,109 --> 00:31:18,909
That man is scary.

721
00:31:20,750 --> 00:31:22,429
Getting a divorce is not that easy.

722
00:31:30,189 --> 00:31:31,030
You're back, madam.

723
00:31:35,829 --> 00:31:37,629
Are you eating dinner at home?

724
00:32:03,629 --> 00:32:04,429
What are you doing?

725
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:13,470
What are you planning?

726
00:32:15,030 --> 00:32:15,710
Jiang Hongbin.

727
00:32:16,950 --> 00:32:18,149
I'm not coming back.

728
00:32:19,429 --> 00:32:20,189
If you won't agree

729
00:32:20,189 --> 00:32:21,270
to getting a divorce,

730
00:32:21,790 --> 00:32:22,990
I'll get my lawyer talk to you.

731
00:32:25,470 --> 00:32:27,109
Are you really going to carry on
with your antics?

732
00:32:27,349 --> 00:32:28,629
What antics?

733
00:32:28,950 --> 00:32:30,070
You used Xu Miao

734
00:32:30,189 --> 00:32:31,429
to pressure me, control me.

735
00:32:31,510 --> 00:32:33,270
You're forcing me
to come back and beg you.

736
00:32:34,189 --> 00:32:34,790
I'll tell you right now,

737
00:32:34,869 --> 00:32:36,349
you're not going
to get your way this time.

738
00:32:36,950 --> 00:32:37,750
Xu Miao has been released.

739
00:32:38,189 --> 00:32:38,950
She is fine.

740
00:32:39,429 --> 00:32:41,030
I've also closed the studio.

741
00:32:41,710 --> 00:32:43,149
I don't have anything anymore.

742
00:32:44,829 --> 00:32:46,149
I'm going to file for a divorce.

743
00:32:46,310 --> 00:32:47,429
You won't control me any longer.

744
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:49,589
Was I controlling you?

745
00:32:51,149 --> 00:32:52,389
I'm just showing you care.

746
00:32:52,669 --> 00:32:53,710
Why can't you

747
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,990
be like other women?

748
00:32:55,230 --> 00:32:56,470
Stay at home

749
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,349
and be a good mother,

750
00:32:57,389 --> 00:32:58,429
a good wife.

751
00:32:58,550 --> 00:32:59,629
After all that has happened,

752
00:32:59,669 --> 00:33:01,550
this is what you're going to say?

753
00:33:02,710 --> 00:33:04,550
You got my friend in trouble!

754
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:06,750
And now you want me to be a good wife

755
00:33:06,869 --> 00:33:07,829
and mother?

756
00:33:08,589 --> 00:33:09,070
There's no way

757
00:33:09,149 --> 00:33:10,189
I'd spend my life with you,

758
00:33:10,230 --> 00:33:10,829
let alone

759
00:33:10,869 --> 00:33:12,629
bear a child for such a person!

760
00:33:12,909 --> 00:33:13,629
Such a person?

761
00:33:14,070 --> 00:33:14,869
What's wrong with me?

762
00:33:15,750 --> 00:33:16,750
I spend money to look after you,

763
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:18,070
make you happy.

764
00:33:18,389 --> 00:33:19,990
And now you claim I'm controlling you!

765
00:33:20,470 --> 00:33:21,909
Do you have to torture me like this?

766
00:33:22,070 --> 00:33:22,869
Piss me off?

767
00:33:22,990 --> 00:33:23,510
Jiang Hongbin,

768
00:33:23,510 --> 00:33:24,710
your thinking is twisted,

769
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:25,550
you know that?

770
00:33:27,030 --> 00:33:28,349
You're a madman.

771
00:33:30,990 --> 00:33:31,669
Step aside.

772
00:33:32,950 --> 00:33:33,629
Get back here!

773
00:33:35,829 --> 00:33:36,629
Jiang Hongbin!

774
00:33:39,869 --> 00:33:40,909
I'm a madman?

775
00:33:42,669 --> 00:33:44,389
I'll show you what mad is.

776
00:33:44,829 --> 00:33:45,710
Jiaqiao!

777
00:33:46,470 --> 00:33:47,310
Ms. He!

778
00:33:49,470 --> 00:33:50,990
Jiang Hongbin, you beast!

779
00:33:53,270 --> 00:33:54,189
Ms. He!

780
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:55,710
Jiaqiao!

781
00:34:01,270 --> 00:34:02,189
The more you resist,

782
00:34:02,189 --> 00:34:03,349
