783
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:05,589
Help!

784
00:34:06,230 --> 00:34:07,189
Jiaqiao!

785
00:34:54,789 --> 00:34:55,550
Madam.

786
00:34:57,510 --> 00:34:58,269
Madam?

787
00:35:00,950 --> 00:35:02,350
Mr. Jiang said he's hungry.

788
00:35:02,830 --> 00:35:04,870
He wants you to make him
lotus seed soup.

789
00:35:07,189 --> 00:35:08,350
Mr. Jiang said yours

790
00:35:08,470 --> 00:35:10,030
is more delicious than what we make.

791
00:35:11,950 --> 00:35:12,870
I've soaked

792
00:35:12,990 --> 00:35:14,350
the lotus seed
and snow fungus for you, madam.

793
00:35:14,629 --> 00:35:15,269
Once it's ready,

794
00:35:15,470 --> 00:35:16,749
you can serve it to him.

795
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:18,430
He's waiting for you in the study.

796
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:40,707
(Qianjin Internet of Things)

797
00:35:40,709 --> 00:35:41,309
Okay, got it.

798
00:35:41,789 --> 00:35:42,350
No problem.

799
00:35:42,510 --> 00:35:43,309
Rest assured.

800
00:35:44,470 --> 00:35:44,950
Okay.

801
00:35:45,109 --> 00:35:45,910
I'm on my way.

802
00:35:47,589 --> 00:35:48,269
How is it?

803
00:35:51,070 --> 00:35:51,910
Perfect.

804
00:35:55,149 --> 00:35:56,629
I need to be recompensed
for these liver protection tablets.

805
00:35:58,749 --> 00:35:59,629
The result is out.

806
00:36:00,309 --> 00:36:02,229
Hongjiang Group won the bid.

807
00:36:02,510 --> 00:36:03,470
Really?

808
00:36:04,629 --> 00:36:06,070
