811
00:36:11,390 --> 00:36:12,229
Nice.

812
00:36:13,189 --> 00:36:13,749
Now,

813
00:36:13,870 --> 00:36:15,269
we better hurry up on recruiting

814
00:36:15,269 --> 00:36:15,990
and get to work.

815
00:36:17,629 --> 00:36:18,950
I've been thinking,

816
00:36:19,030 --> 00:36:20,109
if everything goes well,

817
00:36:20,109 --> 00:36:21,189
I'd like to bring Yuanyuan

818
00:36:21,269 --> 00:36:21,830
and Huang Chong over.

819
00:36:21,910 --> 00:36:22,709
What do you think?

820
00:36:23,070 --> 00:36:24,629
Great minds think alike.

821
00:36:25,430 --> 00:36:26,070
In a battle,

822
00:36:26,149 --> 00:36:27,789
