you know and trust.

823
00:36:28,830 --> 00:36:29,350
Okay.

824
00:36:29,870 --> 00:36:30,589
I have to hurry.

825
00:36:30,749 --> 00:36:31,749
Mr. Jiang is waiting for me.

826
00:36:32,430 --> 00:36:33,269
Off to battle I go.

827
00:36:34,669 --> 00:36:35,990
Call for a driver if you're drinking.

828
00:36:36,709 --> 00:36:37,430
Don't worry.

829
00:36:54,269 --> 00:36:55,589
Madam, are you hungry?

830
00:36:55,789 --> 00:36:57,189
Whatever you want to eat,
I can make it for you.

831
00:36:57,510 --> 00:36:58,149
Madam.

832
00:36:58,789 --> 00:36:59,309
Madam.

833
00:36:59,589 --> 00:37:00,550
You can't leave.

834
00:37:00,589 --> 00:37:01,189
Madam.

835
00:37:02,149 --> 00:37:03,669
Mr. Jiang gave orders.

836
00:37:03,789 --> 00:37:04,789
You should rest at home.

837
00:37:04,830 --> 00:37:05,789
You're not allowed to go out, madam.

838
00:37:05,830 --> 00:37:06,550
Xiang Nan.

839
00:37:07,189 --> 00:37:07,789
Miss.

840
00:37:08,789 --> 00:37:09,950
Where are you going, Xiang Nan?

841
00:37:14,629 --> 00:37:15,229
No!

842
00:37:16,030 --> 00:37:17,189
Ms. He, let her go.

843
00:37:32,350 --> 00:37:32,870
Madam!

844
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:37,430
Who are you calling?

845
00:37:37,870 --> 00:37:38,950
I'm calling Mr. Jiang.

846
00:37:38,950 --> 00:37:39,550
No, don't.

847
00:37:39,709 --> 00:37:40,669
If he asks,

848
00:37:41,589 --> 00:37:42,669
