849
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:09,800
(Jiang Hongbin)

850
00:38:38,669 --> 00:38:39,430
Hello.

851
00:38:40,309 --> 00:38:41,189
Dr. Liang,

852
00:38:41,390 --> 00:38:42,309
the doctor

853
00:38:42,309 --> 00:38:43,910
