855
00:38:45,830 --> 00:38:47,350
if you need any help.

856
00:38:51,390 --> 00:38:52,709
If you do,

857
00:38:53,309 --> 00:38:54,669
we can call the police for you.

858
00:38:59,870 --> 00:39:00,470
No.

859
00:39:01,390 --> 00:39:02,350
Thank you.

860
00:39:05,910 --> 00:39:07,070
If there's a need,

861
00:39:07,149 --> 00:39:07,709
you can

862
00:39:07,709 --> 00:39:09,070
call the number stated.

863
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:12,160
(Say no to domestic violence)

864
00:39:28,030 --> 00:39:28,669
Thanks.

865
00:39:53,749 --> 00:39:54,589
Where were you

866
00:39:54,669 --> 00:39:55,470
in between 4 and 6 PM

867
00:39:55,669 --> 00:39:56,309
on the 3rd of July?

868
00:39:57,550 --> 00:39:58,229
At home.

869
00:39:59,350 --> 00:40:00,950
Is that the usual time you get home?

870
00:40:02,149 --> 00:40:03,470
I own my company.

